org.jclouds.dynect.v3.domain.rdata

Class SOAData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingObject
      • com.google.common.collect.ForwardingMap<String,Object>
        • org.jclouds.dynect.v3.domain.rdata.SOAData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Map<String,Object>

    public class SOAData
extends com.google.common.collect.ForwardingMap<String,Object>
    Corresponds to the binary representation of the SOA (Start of Authority) RData

    Example

     SOAData rdata = SOAData.builder()
                        .rname("foo.com.")
                        .mname("admin.foo.com.")
                        .serial(1)
                        .refresh(3600)
                        .retry(600)
                        .expire(604800)
                        .minimum(60).build()
    See Also:
    RFC 1035
